Update the repository's addCardToCollection method to use Prisma's upsert operation instead of create:

```typescript
async addCardToCollection(userId: number, cardId: string, status: OwnershipStatus = 'OWNED'): Promise<void> {
  await this.db.cardOwnership.upsert({
    where: {
      userId_cardId: {
        userId,
        cardId
      }
    },
    update: {
      status
    },
    create: {
      userId,
      cardId,
      status
    }
  });
}
```

This ensures that existing NOT_NEEDED records can be properly upgraded to OWNED status.

